omosexuals? In some people's minds yes in others acceptance of them is a sin in itself. Which group is sinning? Those who propogate hate in the name of God or those who support immorality in the name of God. The answer depends on your interpretation. The true problem however, comes when forcing your personal interpretation onto others.<br>
<br>
Am I less Christian because I choose not to associate with an organized form of religion. I don't know and I don't care. I have my personal code of ethics that I use to apply to my own life. I follow Christian ways probably closer than the average (note- I did not say all or even most) church goer. If however they are closer to God so be it. I will lose no sleep over it. I know what I believe a good person should be and try to achieve those standards in my own life. If others did that first I may not be so offended by the current state of organized religions<br>
<br>
Ritt<br>
